<subSubSection id="E1DE65590532FFCB889EFCB51797F1B5" pageId="3" pageNumber="300" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="A97B36D20532FFCB889EFCB51797F1B5" blockId="3.[151,1437,785,919]" pageId="3" pageNumber="300">
The four species that comprise this species-group were described after the genus review by 
<bibRefCitation id="CD554B230532FFCB8C80FCB612EFF109" author="Moore, T. &amp; Lander, T." box="[1161,1433,785,812]" pageId="3" pageNumber="300" refId="ref2181" refString="Moore, T. &amp; Lander, T. (2010) Revision du genre Conognatha. Magellanes, Andresy, 170 pp." type="book" year="2010">Moore &amp; Lander (2010)</bibRefCitation>
. 
<bibRefCitation id="CD554B230532FFCB889EFC9116A1F16D" author="Portela, C. &amp; Mermudes, J. R. M." box="[151,471,821,847]" pageId="3" pageNumber="300" pagination="114 - 124" refId="ref2269" refString="Portela, C. &amp; Mermudes, J. R. M. (2014) Two new species of Conognatha Eschscholtz, 1829 (Coleoptera, Buprestidae, Stigmoderini) from Southeast and South Brazilian regions with distributional notes. Zootaxa, 3857 (1), 114 - 124. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 3857.1.5" type="journal article" year="2014">Portela &amp; Mermudes (2014)</bibRefCitation>
made modifications to couplet 48 of the key proposed by 
<bibRefCitation id="CD554B230532FFCB8C64FC921209F16D" author="Moore, T. &amp; Lander, T." box="[1133,1407,821,848]" pageId="3" pageNumber="300" refId="ref2181" refString="Moore, T. &amp; Lander, T. (2010) Revision du genre Conognatha. Magellanes, Andresy, 170 pp." type="book" year="2010">Moore &amp; Lander (2010)</bibRefCitation>
to include the new species. A simplified identification key for the 
<taxonomicName id="6EC44D510532FFCB8B5DFCFD1303F151" authorityName="Pineda &amp; Koike &amp; Barros" authorityYear="2022" box="[852,1141,857,884]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Conognatha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="300" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="continua" subGenus="Pithiscus">
<emphasis id="9BB0EAC00532FFCB8B5DFCFD14A8F151" box="[852,990,857,883]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="300">Conognatha</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="9BB0EAC00532FFCB8BE7FCFE1372F151" box="[1006,1028,858,883]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="300">P.</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis id="9BB0EAC00532FFCB8C1AFCFE1303F151" box="[1043,1141,858,883]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="300">continua</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species-group is proposed below.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
